						               													<description>Unleash spectacular combos and devastating finishing moves in this jaw-dropping, butt-kicking fighting game of martial arts mash-ups! For 2-4 players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Samurai Punk, players assume the role of deadly warriors in an original world that blends steampunk with martial arts - samurais, ninjas, kung-fu monks, gangsters, gunslingers, knights templar, and more! Combining a Fighter deck and a Sensei deck, players create a unique fighting duo to duel against their opponents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Combos are formed by pairing a sensei's Style cards with a fighter's Strike cards, creating one of thousands of different moves, like &amp;quot;Flying Kick&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fierce Defensive Slash&amp;quot;, and &amp;quot;Ultra Spinning Dragon Uppercut&amp;quot;. Each round, new Styles or Strikes are played, replacing some cards in the players' Combos while retaining the others. Used cards store up Chi energy which can activate special abilities, making every card count. Master your duo's unique strategies and versatile combos to out-fight your opponents to victory!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
